Crafting




MBI Equities
An approach designed to navigate through multiple market cycles. 



MBI Quantitative
A complement to fundamental strategies with a proven track record. 



MBI Fixed Income
Simple but effective solutions, engineered to manage risk, preserve capital and add value. 


Partnering




MBI/TEC Private Debt Opportunities Fund
Private debt: An absolute return solution with low correlation to markets. 



MBI/TGA Emerging Market Equities
Access to equity investment opportunities in Developed and Emerging Markets to benefit from Emerging Market Wealth. 












