PHILADELPHIA, June 22, 2017 /PRNewswire/ -- Aberdeen Emerging Markets Smaller Company Opportunities Fund, Inc.1 (the "Fund") (NYSE MKT: ABE)2, a closed-end equity fund, announced today its performance data and portfolio composition as of May 31, 2017. 
The Fund's total returns for various periods through May 31, 2017 are provided below.  (All figures are based on distributions reinvested at the dividend reinvestment price and are stated net-of-fees):  













